Boehner Says He’ll Pursue Smaller Deficit Reduction Deal With White House

-- B y   P a u l   T i g h e
-- 
2011-07-10T00:31:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-10/boehner-says-he-ll-pursue-smaller-deficit-reduction-deal-with-white-house.html
House Speaker  John Boehner  said he
will pursue a smaller deficit reduction accord because the White
House won’t approve a bigger debt reduction deal without tax
increases.  “I believe the best approach may be to focus on producing
a smaller measure,” Boehner said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Tighe at 
 ptighe@bloomberg.net  